condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Accounting software (Financing Agreement - Schedule 2.II.B.4a) | Description :The Recipient shall cause theProject Implementing Entity to, not later than three (3) months after the Effective Date, set up an accounting software forfinancial management of the Project. | Due Date : Three months after effectiveness

Finance Agreement :Appointment of an external auditor (Financing Agreement - Schedule 2.II.B.4b) | Description :The Recipient shallcause the Project Implementing Entity to, not later than six (6) months after the Effective Date, recruit an external auditor inaccordance with the provisions of Section III of Schedule 2 of the Financing Agreement. | Due Date :Six months after effectiveness

Finance Agreement :Steering Committee (Financing Agreement - Schedule 2.I.A.1a) | Description :Not later than three months afterthe Effective Date, the Recipient shall establish, and thereafter maintain, throughout the implementation of the Project, asteering committee ("Steering Committee"), with a composition, mandate, and resources satisfactory to the Association. | Due Date:Three months after effectiveness
